data.description: Stunning newly built custom home in a dream, wooded location. Conveniently located within thirty minutes of Dayton or Columbus, this location is even more amazing when you discover the level of peacefulness and privacy within minutes of exiting the highway. A cedar arched covered porch cheerfully welcomes all to the home. Natural light streams through the double side lights & transom window surrounding the front door. Engineered hardwood floors run throughout the majority of the main level enhancing the much desired, open concept layout. The kitchen, being the heart of every home, features built-on-site custom cabinetry and is anchored by a 10' center island. Featuring gorgeous Cambria Quartz counters, tiled, accented backsplash, brushed nickel pulls, farm sink and SS appliances, combine to create a space that inspires. Behind the frosted glass door at the edge of the kitchen, hides a stylish 7x6 walk-in pantry w/weathered hardwood shelving and a cleverly located coffee bar. The primary bedroom offers more design touches w/an accent wall, industrial style light fixtures, and engineered hardwood flooring. Continuing into an indulgent private bath featuring porcelain tile floors, custom built double vanities, quartz counters, the tiled shower, and a 13x9 walk-in closet! Bonus - the primary bath is just a pocket door away to one of two entrances to the laundry. How convenient! Two more bedrooms and a charmingly appointed guest bath are on this floor. Modern metal railing encloses the stairway leading to the full basement. Unfinished, but primed to be finished w/two egress windows and a 3-piece bath rough-in. Major mechanicals include Geo-thermal heating & cooling, 50-gallon water heater, and 2022 commercial grade water softener. In addition, the house has also been fitted with a transfer switch & exterior connection site for a mobile generator. Covered rear porch & still more details to name! Schedule to see this lovely home soon!
